creator: Subsplash Inc
descriptionHtml:
First Baptist Church Clinton exists to fulfill the great commission by loving people into a growing relationship with Jesus. The First Baptist Church of Clinton app connects you to a variety of resources, including messages, music, videos, event information and more.

Features:

Media
- Hear Sunday sermons from our pastor and guest speakers
- Listen to music from our instrumentalists, vocalists and choir
- Watch videos from special events and mission trips

Connect
- Get up-to-date news and event information
- Share prayer needs and read others requests and stories
- Discover ways you can get connected to our church through Bible studies, missions and serving

For more information about First Baptist Church of Clinton, please visit our website at http://firstbaptistclinton.church
descriptionShort: The official app for First Baptist Church of Clinton, Missouri

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- You can now reorder your media downloads to listen in the order you want.
- Media search has been removed from the app header and is now in the left navigation menu.
- Messaging now loads faster!
- Better support for Subsplash Live.
- Fixed several issues where push notifications were not opening Messaging correctly.
- Fixed issue where messages were appearing in the wrong channel.
